        <h1>How do I create a suppression rule from the web interface?</h1>
        <br>
        <br>
        <center>
            <table border="1" width="80%">
                <tr>
                    <td valign="top">1.</td>
                    <td>
                        Go the the EEB portal and login.  You should be able to login with your Windows username/password.
                        <br>
                        <br>
                        <img src="../../login.png">
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td valign="top">2.</td>
                    <td>
                        Navigate to the Throttle page.
                        <br>
                        <br>
                        <img src="../../navigate_throttle.png">
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td valign="top">3.</td>
                    <td>
                        Click on "Add Rule" link, and fill in all the pertinent information.
                        <br>
                        <br>
                        <img src="add_rule.png">
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td valign="top">4.</td>
                    <td>
                        It is recommended that 1 rule be added for each of the storm levels (total 3 rules).
                        <br>
                        <br>
                        <img src="storm_levels.png">
                    </td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </center>
